window.bookSummaryJSON = "One of the unquestioned masters of military science fiction, <i>New York Times</i> best-selling author John Ringo teams with real-life rocket scientist Travis S. Taylor for this action-packed sequel to <i>Into the Looking Glass</i>. The alien Dreen are still a terrifying menace across the galaxy, but Earth has a new weapon - the first human warp ship. Aboard the Vorpal Blade, America's tough-as-nails Force Recon Marines seek the Dreen, hoping to bring the fight directly to them."; 
